  </li>
  <li>
    <p>1 Molar HCl (for testing effervescence in the field)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Deionised water</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
      <u>Black</u> tray for dispersion and slaking tests (e.g. pot plant tray
      10–15 cm in diameter).
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
      Trimble® R1 (GNSS receiver with sub-metre accuracy and Bluetooth
      connectivity)
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
      Australian Soil and Land Classification Handbook (Yellow Book; The
      National Committee on Soil and Terrain 2009)
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Munsell Soil Colour Charts (Munsell Color 2009)</p>
  </li>
