    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
      Repeat steps 9–12 for each 10 cm soil depth increment in the horizon that
      you are collecting a sample from.
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Repeat steps 5–13 for each soil horizon down to a depth of 1 m+.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Record any Additional soil pit characterisation comments.</p>
  </li>
  <li><p>Store all samples together in a large plastic bag.</p></li>
